org.apache.lucene.store

Class IndexOutput

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.lucene.store.DataOutput
      • org.apache.lucene.store.IndexOutput
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ByteBuffersIndexOutput, OutputStreamIndexOutput, RAMOutputStream, RateLimitedIndexOutput

    public abstract class IndexOutput
extends DataOutput
implements Closeable
    A DataOutput for appending data to a file in a Directory. Instances of this class are not thread-safe.
    See Also:
    Directory, IndexInput
